WEBVTT

00:02.268 --> 00:03.770
<i>PREVIOUSLY ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

00:03.770 --> 00:05.539
WHEN THEY WERE BOOKING ME,
I TOLD THEM THAT WYATT DID IT.

00:05.539 --> 00:07.207
YOU DID?
YES, I DID.

00:07.207 --> 00:08.408
THEY WILL PROCESS YOU,

00:08.408 --> 00:10.611
AND I'LL HAVE YOU OUT
IN A MATTER OF HOURS.

00:10.611 --> 00:13.279
WHAT WOULD AMANDA
BE NEEDING A GUN FOR?

00:13.279 --> 00:14.548
SHE WANTS US DEAD.

00:14.548 --> 00:17.017
JEFFERY.
OH. YOU KNOW MY SON.

00:17.884 --> 00:19.485
JIM'S GONNA BE A DADDY AGAIN.

00:19.485 --> 00:22.055
I'M CARRYING A CRYER.

00:22.055 --> 00:24.257
YOU HAVE JUST
OFFICIALLY BECOME MY ENEMY.

00:24.257 --> 00:26.560
YOU CAN'T AFFORD ME
AS AN ENEMY.

00:26.560 --> 00:30.564
YOU'RE RIGHT.
[ MUFFLED SCREAMING ]

00:30.564 --> 00:33.099
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

00:41.742 --> 00:43.577
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE,
HANNA?

00:45.912 --> 00:49.950
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?

00:49.950 --> 00:52.085
I'M SORRY.

00:52.085 --> 00:54.655
[ Voice breaking ]
YOU TOLD THE POLICE?

00:58.024 --> 00:59.225
MRS. CRYER.

01:01.635 --> 01:03.537
WHAT DID YOU TELL THEM?

01:03.537 --> 01:07.541
I TOLD THEM WHAT I SAW.

01:07.541 --> 01:10.944
HANNA. WHY?

01:10.944 --> 01:13.947
I'M SORRY, MRS. CRYER.

01:13.947 --> 01:19.786
BUT I CAN'T SACRIFICE MY SON
FOR YOURS...

01:19.786 --> 01:22.455
NO MATTER WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO HELP HIM.

01:26.660 --> 01:28.995
HANNA YOUNG?

01:28.995 --> 01:30.931
YES.
YOU'RE FREE TO GO.

01:30.931 --> 01:32.599
HERE ARE YOUR THINGS.

01:32.599 --> 01:33.867
THANK YOU.

01:33.867 --> 01:36.236
MUST HAVE
SOME POWERFUL FRIENDS.

01:43.577 --> 01:45.946
I THINK I USED TO.

01:48.515 --> 01:52.485
MRS. CRYER.

01:52.485 --> 01:54.487
I'M SORRY.

01:54.487 --> 01:57.691
HANNA, I DON'T WANT
TO TALK ABOUT THIS.

01:57.691 --> 01:59.225
I KNOW YOU'RE UPSET.

01:59.225 --> 02:01.502
[ SCOFFS ]

02:01.502 --> 02:05.371
THIS IS MY SON.
AND WYATT IS MY SON.

02:05.371 --> 02:09.075
SO, I WASN'T SUPPOSED
TO SAY ANYTHING?

02:09.075 --> 02:12.746
I THOUGHT YOU WOULDN'T.

02:12.746 --> 02:17.250
YOU THOUGHT WRONG.

02:17.250 --> 02:21.855
YOU SHOULD GO.

02:21.855 --> 02:26.527
I SAW THE SKETCH ON TV.

02:26.527 --> 02:30.647
AND I KNOW YOUR HUSBAND TRIED
TO MAKE ME THINK I WAS CRAZY.

02:32.533 --> 02:35.068
BUT I CAN'T DO THIS.

02:37.203 --> 02:39.740
YOU'RE ASKING ME
TO UNDERSTAND THAT?

02:39.740 --> 02:41.341
YES.

02:44.077 --> 02:46.747
I'M SORRY, HANNA.

02:46.747 --> 02:50.751
I HAVE TO TELL THE TRUTH.

02:50.751 --> 02:54.588
YOU WOULDN'T EXPECT
ANYTHING LESS FROM ME.

02:54.588 --> 02:57.123
[ SNIFFLES ] NO.

02:57.123 --> 03:00.100
ACTUALLY, I EXPECTED MORE.

03:02.703 --> 03:05.706
WELL, I'M SORRY
TO DISAPPOINT YOU,

03:05.706 --> 03:08.542
BUT I WON'T BE
A PART OF THAT.

03:08.542 --> 03:10.043
I CAN'T.

03:13.847 --> 03:16.850
