15:02.836 --> 15:05.338
MM‐HMM.
OH, YOU'RE SURE.

15:05.338 --> 15:06.640
YES.

15:11.211 --> 15:14.380
[ SIGHS ] I KNOW YOU.

15:14.380 --> 15:17.117
WHAT DID YOU DO
TO JEFFERY?

15:17.117 --> 15:19.786
HE'S JUST COMING AROUND.

15:19.786 --> 15:22.288
NO, VERONICA,
HE IS NOT JUST COMING AROUND.

15:22.288 --> 15:25.992
HE'S COMING OUT, FINALLY FINDING
THE STRENGTH TO BE WHO HE IS,

15:25.992 --> 15:28.361
AND YOU DID SOMETHING
TO MAKE HIM CHANGE.

15:28.361 --> 15:30.864
I SURE HOPE SO.

15:30.864 --> 15:33.499
WHAT IS IT?

15:33.499 --> 15:35.836
