15:35.836 --> 15:37.938
WELL, ONE WAY OR ANOTHER,
I'LL FIND OUT.

15:37.938 --> 15:39.940
GOOD.

15:39.940 --> 15:42.008
WHAT HAS GOTTEN INTO YOU?

15:42.008 --> 15:43.744
EXCUSE ME?

15:47.180 --> 15:52.152
YOU USED TO BE SO ‐‐
[SIGHS] SO LOVING, SWEET ‐‐

15:52.152 --> 15:54.888
I MEAN,
ALWAYS A LITTLE CONTROLLING,

15:54.888 --> 15:57.223
BUT NEVER THIS.

15:57.223 --> 15:59.626
