AGAINST THE WALL.

16:12.513 --> 16:14.848
NO, JEFFERY IS NOT PUSHING YOU
AGAINST THE WALL.

16:14.848 --> 16:16.249
DAVID, PLEASE.

16:16.249 --> 16:17.551
NO, VERONICA.

16:17.551 --> 16:19.352
THE ONLY TIME
WE'VE EVER REALLY FOUGHT

16:19.352 --> 16:22.055
WAS WHEN YOU WERE GOING THROUGH
YOUR ADDICTION TO PAIN PILLS.

16:22.055 --> 16:23.590
AND YOU BRING
THIS UP NOW? WHY?

16:23.590 --> 16:24.825
BECAUSE WE'RE ABOUT
TO HAVE A REALLY BAD ONE.

16:24.825 --> 16:25.926
IS THAT SO?
THAT IS SO.

16:25.926 --> 16:27.528
I WILL NOT TOLERATE THIS.

16:27.528 --> 16:30.396
YOUR BEHAVIOR IS GONNA CREATE
SOME SERIOUS PROBLEMS FOR US!

16:30.396 --> 16:32.566
