16:46.980 --> 16:48.782
WHO ‐‐ WHO ARE YOU NOW?

16:48.782 --> 16:51.718
W‐WHO IS ‐‐ WHO IS THIS ‐‐
THIS PRO‐GAY,

16:51.718 --> 16:53.887
"I'M ‐‐ I'M UPSTANDING,
I'M HONEST"?

16:53.887 --> 16:56.089
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
I AM JEFFERY'S FATHER!

16:56.089 --> 16:57.423
AND I AM JEFFERY'S MOTHER!

16:57.423 --> 16:59.459
THEN ACT LIKE IT, DAMN IT!

16:59.459 --> 17:02.035
DON'T YOU DARE
INSULT ME.

17:02.035 --> 17:04.404
WHY NOT? YOU'RE DOING IT
TO EVERYBODY ELSE.

17:07.007 --> 17:09.342
FINE.

17:09.342 --> 17:13.580
YOU ENJOY YOUR STAY
IN THE GUEST ROOM.

17:13.580 --> 17:16.750
GLADLY.

17:16.750 --> 17:21.254
