YOU GOT HER NUMBER.

17:44.444 --> 17:46.112
YEP.

17:46.112 --> 17:48.448
SO YOU'RE GOING
TO TAKE HER ON A DATE?

17:48.448 --> 17:50.483
MAYBE.
GREAT.

17:50.483 --> 17:52.553
MAYBE YOU TWO
CAN GET YOUR NAILS DONE.

17:56.890 --> 17:57.924
GO TO HELL.

17:57.924 --> 18:00.260
SORRY. HOLD ON.

18:00.260 --> 18:01.768
I'M SORRY.

18:01.768 --> 18:03.737
