18:03.737 --> 18:05.906
YEAH, YOU'RE RIGHT.

18:05.906 --> 18:07.941
I'M JUST...

18:10.544 --> 18:12.178
OKAY, LOOK, I LIKE YOU.

18:12.178 --> 18:14.114
YOU DON'T KNOW ME.
BUT I WANT TO.

18:14.114 --> 18:15.181
WHY?

18:15.181 --> 18:20.521
YOU SEEM TO BE
A REALLY NICE GUY, AND...

18:20.521 --> 18:24.525
YOU'RE REALLY SEXY
AND A LITTLE GREEN.

18:24.525 --> 18:26.993
[ SIGHS ]
A LOT GREEN.

18:26.993 --> 18:28.662
ALL RIGHT, UM...

18:28.662 --> 18:31.665
AND THIS IS JUST A LITTLE
TOO MUCH FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

18:31.665 --> 18:34.100
I UNDERSTAND THAT,
BUT YOU CAN'T RUN FROM IT.

18:34.100 --> 18:37.771
NO, I'M NOT RUNNING FROM IT.
I JUST ‐‐ I JUST CAN'T ‐‐

18:37.771 --> 18:39.139
WHAT? YOUR MOM?

18:39.139 --> 18:41.174
[ SIGHS ]

18:46.112 --> 18:48.448
I'VE NEVER BEEN WITH A GIRL,
[Chuckling] OKAY?

18:48.448 --> 18:54.287
SO MAYBE I SHOULD GIVE THAT
A TRY BEFORE I'M SURE.

18:54.287 --> 18:56.790
