19:07.808 --> 19:10.476
BEING WITH A GIRL
WON'T CHANGE WHO YOU ARE.

19:10.476 --> 19:12.746
HAVE YOU EVER BEEN ATTRACTED
TO A GIRL, JEFFERY?

19:12.746 --> 19:14.114
YES.

19:14.114 --> 19:17.283
NO, I'M NOT TALKING BECAUSE SHE
HAS NICE PURSE OR NICE SHOES.

19:17.283 --> 19:19.853
