ISN'T SOMETHING YOU TRY.

19:32.866 --> 19:34.234
IT JUST IS.

19:34.234 --> 19:37.871
WELL, I HAVE TO TRY.

19:37.871 --> 19:39.740
IS THIS YOUR MOTHER,
TOO?

19:41.842 --> 19:43.877
I'LL TAKE THAT AS A YES.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

19:43.877 --> 19:46.513
IF YOU DECIDE TO BE WITH A GIRL,
YOU WILL BE WASTING YOUR TIME.

19:46.513 --> 19:48.515
WELL,
IT'S MY TIME TO WASTE.

19:48.515 --> 19:50.684
