FOR THE HARD QUESTIONS?

20:01.094 --> 20:03.069
I‐I'M JUST ‐‐ I'M NOT READY
FOR ANY OF THIS.

20:03.069 --> 20:04.204
I'M SORRY.

20:04.204 --> 20:06.206
LANDON, CALL THE TEAM.

20:06.206 --> 20:07.841
