WAS JUST ARRESTED.

20:14.915 --> 20:16.750
FOR WHAT?

20:16.750 --> 20:19.019
THE HIT‐AND‐RUN
OF LITTLE LIZZIE. [ SIGHS ]

20:19.019 --> 20:20.286
WHAT?
YEAH.

20:23.657 --> 20:25.692
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

20:33.700 --> 20:35.736
