21:10.043 --> 21:15.115
DAVID, YOU WILL NOT GIVE OUR SON
PERMISSION TO BE A HOMOSEXUAL.

21:15.115 --> 21:18.484
I WILL NOT TOLERATE
YOU TREATING HIM THIS WAY.

21:18.484 --> 21:20.654
OKAY.

21:20.654 --> 21:22.823
OKAY.

21:22.823 --> 21:25.025
I KNOW WHAT THIS IS.
