21:40.340 --> 21:42.275
SHE SURE AS HELL IS TRYING
TO GET ON TOP OF YOU.

21:42.275 --> 21:43.276
OH.

21:43.276 --> 21:45.011
NOW,
THIS IS TRULY INSANE.

21:45.011 --> 21:48.414
THAT WOMAN WANTS YOU, DAVID.
SHE IS JUST DOING HER JOB.

21:48.414 --> 21:50.183
