IS NOT PART OF IT.

21:50.183 --> 21:52.318
AND SHE'S NOT DOING THAT,
SO WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

21:54.655 --> 21:55.989
DO YOU WANT HER?

21:55.989 --> 21:58.825
[ SCOFFS, CHUCKLES ]

21:58.825 --> 22:00.661
I SEE.

22:00.661 --> 22:02.302
YOU'RE TRYING
TO GET ON MAGGIE

22:02.302 --> 22:05.005
SO WE CAN GET OFF THE MATTER
AT HAND, WHICH IS OUR SON.

22:05.005 --> 22:07.040
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

22:09.275 --> 22:13.113
LET ME GUESS ‐‐
MAGGIE DAY.

22:13.113 --> 22:15.849
WHY IS SHE CALLING HERE
SO LATE?

22:15.849 --> 22:18.519
JUST...
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

22:18.519 --> 22:20.353
WILL YOU JUST GIVE ME
MY PHONE BACK?

22:20.353 --> 22:22.022
HI, MAGGIE.

22:22.022 --> 22:24.190
YES, HE'S RIGHT HERE.

22:24.190 --> 22:26.292
UH, DON'T YOU THINK
IT'S A BIT LATE

22:26.292 --> 22:28.562
