ANOTHER WOMAN'S HUSBAND.

22:28.562 --> 22:32.298
NO, YOU WOULDN'T.

22:32.298 --> 22:33.967
WELL, I WILL HAVE
TO TEACH YOU

22:33.967 --> 22:37.470
