IS REPRESENTED BY COUNSEL.

23:35.569 --> 23:37.571
YES, SIR.
YOU'VE MENTIONED IT.

23:37.571 --> 23:39.439
I WANT TO SEE MY SON,
AND I WANT TO SEE HIM NOW!

23:39.439 --> 23:41.207
THE D.A.
