IN SO MUCH PAIN.

25:34.300 --> 25:37.303
THE GRANDFATHER.

25:37.303 --> 25:38.972
[ SIGHS ]

25:38.972 --> 25:42.308
ALL THEY WANT
IS FOR YOU TO CONFESS.

25:45.512 --> 25:47.347
I HAVE NOTHING TO SAY.

25:47.347 --> 25:49.683
WYATT.

25:49.683 --> 25:52.018
COME ON, MAN.

25:52.018 --> 25:53.954
COME ON.

25:53.954 --> 25:55.889
I CAN HELP YOU.

25:55.889 --> 25:58.458
JUST TELL ME THE TRUTH.
TELL ME WHAT HAPPENED.

26:01.234 --> 26:03.136
