A LOT OF KINDNESS

28:13.947 --> 28:16.750
TO MY FAMILY
WHEN THEY WERE IN NEED.

28:16.750 --> 28:19.920
WE'RE IN HIS DEBT.

28:19.920 --> 28:23.156
YOU ARE IN MY SCOPE.

28:23.156 --> 28:25.926
LET ME OUT OF HERE.

