ANYWHERE IN THE COUNTRY.

29:09.142 --> 29:11.077
BUS TICKET?
YES.

29:11.077 --> 29:13.580
I'M A FIRST CLASS
KIND OF BITCH.

29:13.580 --> 29:16.149
I DON'T DO THE BUS.

29:16.149 --> 29:20.286
YOU LEAVE THIS CITY
AND DISAPPEAR,

29:20.286 --> 29:22.623
ABORT THAT KID,

29:22.623 --> 29:26.727
AND YOU DON'T SPEAK
TO JIM OR AMANDA,

29:26.727 --> 29:28.529
