29:35.836 --> 29:38.839
YOU'RE NOT LISTENING.

29:38.839 --> 29:40.774
OPTION NUMBER TWO ‐‐

29:40.774 --> 29:45.045
YOU STAY HERE,
YOU CONTINUE TO HARASS JIM,

29:45.045 --> 29:49.215
YOU CONTINUE TO FIGHT
FOR AMANDA'S INHERITANCE,

29:49.215 --> 29:52.218
AND WE'LL KILL YOUR MOTHER,

29:52.218 --> 29:54.888
AND THEN
WE'LL KILL YOUR BROTHER,

29:54.888 --> 29:57.157
AND THEN WE'LL KILL YOU.

30:01.201 --> 30:03.704
THAT DOESN'T SCARE ME.

30:03.704 --> 30:07.708
YOU SEE,
MY BROTHER'S ALREADY DEAD.

30:07.708 --> 30:12.212
I CAN'T STAND MY MOTHER,
SO [CHUCKLES] BE MY GUEST.

30:12.212 --> 30:15.215
AND I AIN'T AFRAID TO DIE.

30:15.215 --> 30:19.452
SO I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

30:19.452 --> 30:22.122
OKAY.

30:22.122 --> 30:24.625
I CAN SEE
YOU'RE STILL NOT READY.

30:24.625 --> 30:26.793
WELL,
I'LL HAVE TO COME BACK ‐‐

30:26.793 --> 30:29.596
YOU KNOW, MAYBE IN A WEEK,
A MONTH.

30:29.596 --> 30:31.598
WHO KNOWS?

30:31.598 --> 30:33.266
[ CHUCKLES ]

30:33.266 --> 30:35.268
OH, IT COULD BE

30:35.268 --> 30:38.271
AFTER JIM'S
IN THE GOVERNOR'S MANSION ‐‐

30:38.271 --> 30:41.675
OR IN THE WHITE HOUSE!

30:41.675 --> 30:44.177
YEAH, HE WILL WIN.

30:44.177 --> 30:48.114
I HAVE A VESTED INTEREST
TO MAKE SURE THAT HAPPENS.

30:48.114 --> 30:51.317
SO, IT'S UP TO YOU.

30:51.317 --> 30:55.221
I HOPE YOU'RE NOT AFRAID
OF THE DARK.

31:01.668 --> 31:03.704
[ LIGHT SWITCH CLICKS ]

31:05.772 --> 31:08.775
OHH, JIM.

31:08.775 --> 31:10.443
[ SIGHS ]

31:10.443 --> 31:12.946
YOU HAVE MESSED
WITH THE WRONG ONE ‐‐

31:12.946 --> 31:15.481
THE WRONG ONE.

31:17.751 --> 31:19.620
[ SIGHS ]

31:19.620 --> 31:21.454
[ WHIMPERS ]

31:28.829 --> 31:30.564
[ CRICKETS CHIRPING ]

31:55.288 --> 31:57.290
E‐EXCUSE ME.

31:57.290 --> 31:59.192
UM, HI, I'M ‐‐

31:59.192 --> 32:00.634
HANNA YOUNG.

32:00.634 --> 32:03.103
YES.

32:03.103 --> 32:04.437
WELL,
WE'VE BEEN EXPECTING YOU.

32:04.437 --> 32:06.106
THE DOCTOR'S IN
WITH YOUR SON RIGHT NOW.

32:06.106 --> 32:07.774
OKAY.
COME RIGHT THIS WAY.

32:07.774 --> 32:08.775
THANK YOU.

32:08.775 --> 32:10.777
CAN I GET YOU SOME COFFEE
OR ANYTHING?

32:10.777 --> 32:12.979
NO, THANK YOU. I'M FINE.

32:15.549 --> 32:19.052
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

32:19.052 --> 32:21.955
LORD, LORD, LORD.

32:21.955 --> 32:24.124
HI, I'M DR. BAYLOR.

32:24.124 --> 32:26.727
HI.
YOU MUST BE HANNA YOUNG.

32:26.727 --> 32:29.630
YES, I AM. HOW IS HE?

32:29.630 --> 32:32.032
HE'S STABLE.
NOT MUCH HAS CHANGED.

32:32.032 --> 32:34.835
BUT WE ARE SEEING
SLIGHT BRAIN ACTIVITY.

32:34.835 --> 32:36.837
OH, REALLY?
YES.

32:36.837 --> 32:39.005
OH, JESUS, THANK YOU.

32:39.005 --> 32:41.875
WHAT I'D LIKE TO DO IS START HIM
ON SOME AGGRESSIVE DRUGS

32:41.875 --> 32:44.878
TO REDUCE THE BRAIN EDEMA ‐‐
THE SWELLING.

32:44.878 --> 32:48.214
I THINK IF WE CAN GET
MORE OXYGEN TO HIS BRAIN

32:48.214 --> 32:49.482
BY REDUCING THE SWELLING,

32:49.482 --> 32:51.317
HE MIGHT START
TO BREATHE ON HIS OWN.

32:51.317 --> 32:53.353
WHAT?

32:53.353 --> 32:54.655
NOW, IT'S A LONG SHOT.

32:54.655 --> 32:57.357
I DON'T WANT YOU
TO BECOME TOO HOPEFUL.

32:57.357 --> 32:58.925
BUT I THINK WE SHOULD TRY.

32:58.925 --> 33:00.634
ALL I NEED
IS YOUR PERMISSION.

33:02.969 --> 33:06.006
THEY TOLD ME AT THE COUNTY
THAT THERE WAS NO HOPE.

33:06.006 --> 33:09.175
NO, THAT'S NOT
ALTOGETHER TRUE.

33:09.175 --> 33:11.177
[ SIGHS ]

33:11.177 --> 33:12.879
LORD, THERE'S HOPE.

33:12.879 --> 33:15.248
YES. BUT SLIGHT.

33:15.248 --> 33:17.584
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

33:17.584 --> 33:20.053
ALL I NEED
IS A LITTLE BIT.

33:20.053 --> 33:21.888
THAT'S ALL.

33:21.888 --> 33:25.058
THE SIZE
OF A MUSTARD SEED.

33:25.058 --> 33:27.728
DO IT.

33:27.728 --> 33:29.195
DO IT.

33:29.195 --> 33:32.298
I HAVE TO TELL YOU
THE RISKS.

33:32.298 --> 33:36.036
DR. BAYLOR,
THEY ALREADY HAD ME READY

33:36.036 --> 33:38.772
TO PLAN A FUNERAL
FOR MY CHILD.

33:38.772 --> 33:41.608
THERE ARE NO RISKS.

33:41.608 --> 33:44.110
DO IT.

33:48.148 --> 33:49.916
I'LL GET STARTED
RIGHT AWAY.

33:49.916 --> 33:52.118
THANK YOU.

33:56.156 --> 33:57.824
YOU HEAR THAT, BABY?

33:57.824 --> 33:59.425
YOU HEAR THAT, BABY?

33:59.425 --> 34:02.703
YOU FIGHT, BABY.
YOU FIGHT.

34:02.703 --> 34:05.305
AND WE GOT US SOME HELP.

34:05.305 --> 34:07.641
[ CRYING ]

34:07.641 --> 34:11.645
WE GOT US SOME HELP.

34:11.645 --> 34:14.881
[ SMOOCHES ]

34:30.597 --> 34:31.932
HI.

34:31.932 --> 34:34.100
ANY WORD ON WYATT?
NO. [ SIGHS ]

34:34.100 --> 34:36.002
DAVID, THE D.A.
IS JENNIFER SALISON.

34:36.002 --> 34:37.370
OH, NO.

34:37.370 --> 34:38.705
I KNOW. I KNOW.

34:38.705 --> 34:41.374
SHE HATES US.
YEAH.

34:41.374 --> 34:43.577
SHE LOST THE MALONE CASE
IN MY COURTROOM,

34:43.577 --> 34:45.712
AND SHE'S CARRYING
ONE HELL OF A GRUDGE.

34:45.712 --> 34:48.214
YOU HAVE EVERYTHING
IN PLACE?

34:48.214 --> 34:50.250
YES.

34:52.619 --> 34:53.954
THEN LET'S DO THIS THING.

34:53.954 --> 34:55.556
I'M WITH YOU.

34:55.556 --> 34:56.757
THANKS.

34:56.757 --> 34:59.459
KATHERYN, YOU'RE OKAY?
KATHERYN ‐‐ SHE'S FINE.

35:01.602 --> 35:03.069
HI.
I'M SORRY FOR THIS, JUDGE.

35:03.069 --> 35:04.705
HI.

35:04.705 --> 35:05.839
HELLO.

35:05.839 --> 35:07.974
JIM, ARE YOU OKAY?
YEAH, I'M FINE.

35:07.974 --> 35:09.142
OKAY, GOOD.

35:09.142 --> 35:10.611
ALL RIGHT, THIS IS HOW
WE'RE GONNA MANAGE THIS.

35:10.611 --> 35:11.978
I THINK THAT WE SHOULD ‐‐
N‐NO. STOP, STOP.

35:11.978 --> 35:14.147
I'LL HANDLE IT.
WHAT?

35:14.147 --> 35:17.150
I SAID I'LL HANDLE IT.
I HAVE IT UNDER CONTROL.

35:17.150 --> 35:20.654
OKAY, J‐JIM, I UNDERSTAND
THAT THIS IS AN EMOTIONAL TIME,

35:20.654 --> 35:23.524
BUT THIS COULD DERAIL YOUR HOPES
OF EVER BEING GOVERNOR.

35:23.524 --> 35:25.291
IT HAS TO BE
HANDLED CAREFULLY.

35:25.291 --> 35:26.960
THIS TOWN
IS A POWDER KEG.

35:26.960 --> 35:29.362
THEY ARE
IN AN OUTRAGE OVER THIS,

35:29.362 --> 35:31.264
AND "THIS" BEING YOUR SON.

35:31.264 --> 35:34.835
MAGGIE,
I SAID I'LL HANDLE IT.

35:34.835 --> 35:37.370
HAVE YOU SEEN THE MOB OF PRESS?
THEY'RE AT THE GATE.

35:37.370 --> 35:39.239
YOU NEED
TO LET ME HANDLE THIS.

35:39.239 --> 35:40.907
[ SIGHS ]

35:40.907 --> 35:42.543
ARE YOU NOT LISTENING
TO A WORD I'M SAYING?

35:42.543 --> 35:44.044
LANDON, TELL HIM.

35:44.044 --> 35:45.712
JUST HEAR ME OUT.

35:45.712 --> 35:47.714
WE NEED TO ISSUE A STATEMENT.

35:47.714 --> 35:49.049
I WILL FLOAT IT
TO ALL THE BLOGS.

35:49.049 --> 35:51.384
I WILL GIVE INSIGHT ABOUT
THE STATE OF THE FAMILY

35:51.384 --> 35:53.053
ON BACKGROUND NOT ON RECORD.

35:53.053 --> 35:55.121
WE WILL IN‐‐
ARE YOU FINISHED.

35:55.121 --> 35:56.957
YES.

35:56.957 --> 35:59.259
NO, LANDON.

35:59.259 --> 36:00.400
NO.

36:00.400 --> 36:01.668
JIM.

36:01.668 --> 36:02.936
I'VE GOT IT, MAGGIE.

36:02.936 --> 36:04.270
JIM, THIS IS A CRISIS.

36:04.270 --> 36:05.572
DON'T YOU THINK
I KNOW THAT?

36:05.572 --> 36:07.040
IT'S MY SON
WE'RE TALKING ABOUT.

36:07.040 --> 36:08.775
I'M DEALING WITH THIS,
MAGGIE, NOT YOU.

36:08.775 --> 36:12.445
DAVID,
LET US DO OUR JOB HERE.

36:12.445 --> 36:14.314
PLEASE, PLEASE TALK SOME SENSE
INTO HIM.

36:14.314 --> 36:16.917
NO, MAGGIE, YOU HAVE TO LET US
HANDLE THIS ONE.

36:18.985 --> 36:20.621
WELL, I'M BEING TOLD
BY THE REVEREND

36:20.621 --> 36:22.188
THAT HE'S BANDING TOGETHER
A MARCH

36:22.188 --> 36:23.690
TO HEAD THIS WAY
IN THE MORNING.

36:23.690 --> 36:25.358
MR. CRYER,
YOU SHOULD LISTEN TO HER.

36:25.358 --> 36:27.694
YOU SHOULD LISTEN TO ME.
ALL OF YOU SHOULD LISTEN TO ME.

36:27.694 --> 36:29.395
I'M GONNA HANDLE THIS MY WAY.

36:29.395 --> 36:32.165
OKAY? MY WAY. HEY!

36:32.165 --> 36:34.668
YOUR FIVE MINUTES
WERE UP SIX MINUTES AGO.

36:34.668 --> 36:37.103
NOW, I WANT TO GO IN THERE
AND SEE MY SON RIGHT AWAY,

36:37.103 --> 36:39.039
OR YOU ARE GONNA BECOME
INTIMATELY AWARE

36:39.039 --> 36:41.341
OF THE PHRASE, "WOULD
YOU LIKE FRIES WITH THAT?"

36:42.676 --> 36:44.210
IS THAT THE BASTARD?

36:44.210 --> 36:45.311
SIR, PLEASE.

36:45.311 --> 36:46.747
NO, IS THAT HIM?

36:46.747 --> 36:49.750
THAT'S WHAT
WE'RE TRYING TO FIND OUT.

36:49.750 --> 36:51.652
WHERE'S YOUR DAUGHTER?

36:51.652 --> 36:53.854
SHE SHOULD'VE BEEN HERE
BY NOW.

36:53.854 --> 36:55.789
CAN YOU LOCATE HER?

36:55.789 --> 36:58.124
I CAN ONLY HOLD HIM
FOR SO LONG.

36:58.124 --> 36:59.626
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

36:59.626 --> 37:02.201
[ SIGHS ]
I'LL CALL TO SEE.

37:02.201 --> 37:04.604
HAVE HER HURRY.

37:04.604 --> 37:08.307
MY DAUGHTER
HAS A DRUG PROBLEM.

37:08.307 --> 37:12.679
I'LL TRY TO GET HER
ON THE PHONE.

37:23.690 --> 37:26.059
SO?
YEAH, THE MOTHER'S NOT HERE.

37:26.059 --> 37:27.293
GREAT.

37:27.293 --> 37:29.696
FATHER THINKS SHE'S OUT
GETTING HIGH SOMEWHERE.

37:29.696 --> 37:32.398
THIS FATHER IS GOING
TO SHUT US DOWN IN A SECOND.

37:32.398 --> 37:34.067
YEAH, I KNOW. I KNOW.

37:34.067 --> 37:36.837
TRY HARDER
TO GET A CONFESSION.

37:39.239 --> 37:41.174
IN A FEW SECONDS,
HAVE AN OFFICER COME IN

37:41.174 --> 37:43.443
AND WHISPER
SOMETHING TO ME.

37:43.443 --> 37:45.145
ALL RIGHT?

37:58.659 --> 37:59.993
IS MY DAD OUT THERE?

37:59.993 --> 38:02.335
NO, I DIDN'T SEE HIM.

38:02.335 --> 38:04.505
CAN I CALL HIM?

38:04.505 --> 38:05.772
YEAH.

38:05.772 --> 38:08.775
YEAH, LET ME, UH ‐‐
LET ME GET YOU A PHONE.

38:08.775 --> 38:10.611
HEY, UH,
YOU MUST BE TIRED.

38:10.611 --> 38:12.613
YOU SMOKE?

38:12.613 --> 38:14.715
YEAH.

38:21.321 --> 38:24.725
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

38:30.196 --> 38:32.699
THANKS.

38:32.699 --> 38:35.068
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

38:35.068 --> 38:39.540
YOU'VE JUST BEEN IDENTIFIED
BY THE BABY'S MOTHER.

38:39.540 --> 38:42.108
WHAT?

38:42.108 --> 38:44.477
YEAH.

38:44.477 --> 38:47.648
OKAY, I NEED MY DAD.

38:47.648 --> 38:51.818
YEAH, THAT'S JUST NOT HAPPENING,
NOT RIGHT NOW.

38:51.818 --> 38:54.054
YOU'RE GOING TO JAIL.

38:57.090 --> 38:59.760
NO.

38:59.760 --> 39:02.936
[ SIGHS ] NO.

39:05.471 --> 39:08.642
LOOK, UH,
THAT BABY'S MOTHER,

39:08.642 --> 39:11.978
SHE'S GOING
THROUGH A ROUGH TIME.

39:11.978 --> 39:16.182
DON'T YOU WANT TO HELP HER OUT,
MAKE HER FEEL BETTER?

39:16.182 --> 39:21.522
I KNOW YOU DIDN'T MEAN
TO DO THIS.

39:21.522 --> 39:24.024
JUST TELL ME
WHAT HAPPENED.

39:24.024 --> 39:26.627
LET'S GIVE HER SOME PEACE.

39:30.396 --> 39:32.398
COME ON, WYATT,
I KNOW YOU'RE NOT A BAD GUY.

39:32.398 --> 39:35.235
YOU COME
FROM A GOOD FAMILY.

39:35.235 --> 39:38.271
TALK TO ME
SO I CAN HELP YOU.

39:40.273 --> 39:41.875
ALL RIGHT.

39:41.875 --> 39:44.911
SO, YOU'RE AT A CRACK HOUSE.
YOU'RE GETTING HIGH.

39:50.316 --> 39:51.952
YEAH.

39:51.952 --> 39:55.021
WHAT HAPPENS NEXT?

39:58.158 --> 39:59.826
I DON'T REMEMBER
A LOT OF IT.

39:59.826 --> 40:03.269
ALL RIGHT. ALL RIGHT.

40:03.269 --> 40:06.039
JUST TELL ME
WHAT YOU REMEMBER.

40:09.175 --> 40:11.177
[ SIGHS ]

40:11.177 --> 40:15.181
I WAS WALKING TO MY CAR.

40:15.181 --> 40:18.619
I FELT SOMEONE'S HANDS IN
MY POCKET, SO I GRABBED THEM.

40:18.619 --> 40:21.855
THEN THEY HIT ME.

40:21.855 --> 40:25.125
WHO?

40:25.125 --> 40:27.293
TWO GUYS.

40:27.293 --> 40:29.129
GO ON.

40:29.129 --> 40:32.498
[ SIGHS ]

40:32.498 --> 40:35.335
I FELL.

40:35.335 --> 40:37.403
THEY WERE STOMPING ON ME,

40:37.403 --> 40:42.342
BUT SOMEHOW I MANAGED TO GET UP
AND GET THEM OFF.

40:44.711 --> 40:47.347
I GOT TO THE CAR.

40:47.347 --> 40:50.517
AND THEY WERE HANGING ON,
SO I FLOORED IT.

40:50.517 --> 40:52.986
BLACK SEDAN?

40:56.289 --> 41:00.293
YEAH. BLACK SEDAN.

41:00.293 --> 41:02.769
GO ON.

41:05.906 --> 41:08.609
[ SIGHS ]

41:17.951 --> 41:21.454
[ SIGHS ]

41:31.364 --> 41:33.199
<i>NEXT ON "THE HAVES</i>
<i>AND THE HAVE NOTS"...</i>

41:33.199 --> 41:34.200
JUDGE CRYER.

41:34.200 --> 41:35.936
WHERE IS MY SON?
HE'S BEEN ARRESTED.

41:35.936 --> 41:37.470
I ALREADY TOLD THEM.
You shut up.

41:37.470 --> 41:38.839
WHY DON'T YOU DO US BOTH A FAVOR
AND QUIT?

41:38.839 --> 41:40.541
YOU'D LIKE THAT, WOULDN'T YOU?
WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO TO ME?

41:40.541 --> 41:42.208
WE'RE PREPARING TO GIVE YOU
AN ABORTION.

41:42.208 --> 41:43.610
THIS IS THE PART
OF THE BRAIN RIGHT HERE

41:43.610 --> 41:44.778
THAT CONTROLS THE MOTOR SKILLS.

41:44.778 --> 41:46.847
NOT ABLE TO BREATHE ON HIS OWN,
WILL HE DIE?

41:46.847 --> 41:48.214
CAN IT GO THROUGH
A PROFESSOR?

41:48.214 --> 41:49.550
YOU DON'T WANT
TO KILL A PROFESSOR.

41:49.550 --> 41:51.117
WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO
ABOUT PLAN "A"?

41:51.117 --> 41:52.853
PULL THE TRIGGER.
THAT'S WHAT WE'RE GONNA DO.

41:52.853 --> 41:54.721
THIS IS
AN UGLY BUSINESS, JIM.

41:54.721 --> 41:56.590
YES, IT IS
AN UGLY BUSINESS, DAVID.

41:56.590 --> 41:57.924
I NEED TO FIND AN EX‐CON.

41:57.924 --> 42:00.393
HIS NAME IS NORMAN HUGHIN.

42:00.393 --> 42:01.868
HE'S GONE UNDERGROUND.
